simple stand-alone ESMF MPI test

Notes:
To install and run this case::

./install.sh

To clean this case::

./clean.sh

Folders:
  ./coupledSolver: Source code for the ESMF test case
  ./run: The simulation will run in this folder.

####################
WARNING!!!WARNING!!!
####################
The ESMF should be installed in '../../esmf/' to run this case.
